name: Duckstroma
overview: A game created with the Scorpion Engine by Ultra Narwhal in 2022. it features smooth scrolling, great graphics, multiple enemy types, and much much more! Meet Aura, she's a delivery duck and about to have a life changing day on the job. A client has requested 8 disks be delivered to them, but this won't be an easy task. Using Aura's skills navigate the hostile environment by bouncing on weak foes, even lay an egg to reach higher spots.
